---
// No props needed for this static component
---
<section id="pricing" class="bg-neutral-900 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-200 mb-4">Size Uygun Planı Seçin</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        İster yeni başlıyor olun, ister büyük bir işletme yönetiyor olun, ihtiyaçlarınıza uygun bir çözümümüz var.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center">
      
      <!-- Tier 1: Starter (Hobist) -->
      <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-red-900/50 h-full flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-200 mb-2">Starter</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">Hobist</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 flex-grow">'Yapay zeka dünyasına adım atmak isteyenler için.'</p>
        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-200 mb-6">
          ₺499<span class="text-base font-medium text-gray-500">/ay</span>
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-400 mb-8 flex-grow">
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>1 Adet Flowise Örneği</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Paylaşımlı Kaynaklar</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Günlük Yedekleme</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Standart Destek</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#iletisim" class="block w-full text-center px-6 py-3 bg-transparent border-2 border-red-700 text-red-600 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 hover:text-white transition mt-auto">
          Planı Seç
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Tier 2: Pro (Ajanslar İçin - Highlighted) -->
      <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg shadow-red-700/30 border-2 border-orange-500 relative flex flex-col">
        <div class="absolute top-0 -translate-y-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="px-4 py-1 bg-orange-600 text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full whitespace-nowrap">AJANSLAR İÇİN</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-200 mb-4">Pro</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 flex-grow">Müşterilerine hizmet veren ajanslar için ideal.</p>
        <p class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-200 mb-6">
          ₺999<span class="text-base font-medium text-gray-500">/ay</span>
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-400 mb-8 flex-grow">
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>3 Adet Flowise Örneği</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Özel (Private) Sunucu</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Kendi Domainini Bağla (White Label)</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Öncelikli Destek</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Sınırsız Veri Yükleme</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#iletisim" class="block w-full text-center px-6 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-700 to-orange-600 text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-red-700/20 transition mt-auto">
          Hemen Başla
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Tier 3: Enterprise -->
      <div class="bg-neutral-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-red-900/50 h-full flex flex-col">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-200 mb-4">Enterprise</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 flex-grow">Büyük ölçekli operasyonlar.</p>
        <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-200 mb-6">
          İletişime Geç
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-400 mb-8 flex-grow">
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Sınırsız Örnek</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Özel SLA</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Kurulum Danışmanlığı</li>
           <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Vektör Veritabanı Yönetimi</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="mailto:sales@marssoft.com" class="block w-full text-center px-6 py-3 bg-gray-800 text-gray-200 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-700 transition mt-auto">
          İletişime Geç
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
